reviewText: Loved it could not be better
I obviously am a fan of Duck Dynasty by virtue of buying the Season Four DVD Set.  The quality and delivery can be rated as excellent.

Magnificently edited.  Lovely shots of the pristine, great outdoors.  Need some laughs or an awareness that our culture still has some sane individuals?  This is our favorite show by far since Cosby.  We hope they continue making video productions as long as it is not a stumbling block for them.  Only disappointment with this is that some of the bonus content is clips from episodes already in the season...  Does have some additional deleted scenes.
We love Duck Dynasty !!!!  Greatest show on TV !!!  It's the cleanest show on TV and the prayer at the end says it all !!!
You'll find some of the best Duck Dynasty episodes in this collection!  They are on a roll !!  We love watching over and over...too funny!
